&lt;a href="http://serialized.net/2007/09/quick-lame-tip-concatenate-mp3s/"&gt;else&lt;/a&gt; 
was as frustrated as me. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here's my a bit shorter version of it:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;find&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;mp3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;exec&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;lame&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;decode&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="sc"&gt;&amp;#39;;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;lame&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;b&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;64&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;mp3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary><category term="mp3"></category><category term="lame"></category><category term="command line"></category><category term="tips"></category></entry><entry><title>How to remove unnecessary audio from a video file</title><link href="http://kerma.github.io/remove-audio-from-video.html" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2013-07-30T00:00:00+03:00</updated><author><name>kerma</name></author><id>tag:kerma.github.io,2013-07-30:remove-audio-from-video.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Once in a while I encounter a video file which has more than one audio stream attached to it. Usually
I'm only interested in one of those and want to get rid of the others. Specially if the first one is not
the one I'm interested in. Xbox does provide an easy way to selecting some other stream besides the
first one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So let's fire up avprobe first:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;avprobe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;something_nice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;avi&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;avprobe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;version&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.8.6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.8.6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0u&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;buntu0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;.12.04.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Copyright&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2007&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2013&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Libav&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;developers&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;built&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Apr&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2013&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mo"&gt;00&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;59&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class="n"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;gcc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;4.6.3&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;Input&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;avi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;something_nice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;avi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="nl"&gt;Metadata:&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;encoder&lt;/span&gt;         &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;VirtualDubModRus&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;1.5.10.2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;build&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2542&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;release&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;title&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Something&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Nice&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;artist&lt;/span&gt;          &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Released&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;copyright&lt;/span&gt;       &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;HQ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;ViDEO&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;genre&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Action&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;album&lt;/span&gt;           &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Movie&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;comment&lt;/span&gt;         &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;DVD&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="nl"&gt;Duration:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mo"&gt;01&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;54&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;04.25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.000000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;bitrate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2738&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Stream&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Video&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;mpeg4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Advanced&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Simple&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Profile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;yuv420p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="mi"&gt;720&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;x304&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;PAR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;DAR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;],&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;23.98&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tbr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;23.98&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tbn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;23.98&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;tbc&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Stream&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Audio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ac3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;48000&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Hz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;5.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;s16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;448&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="n"&gt;Stream&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mf"&gt;0.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Audio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ac3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;48000&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;Hz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;5.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;s16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;448&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I'm interested in the second audio stream, which is in the language I understand. avconv helps:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;avconv&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;something_nice&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;avi&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;v&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;copy&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;map&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; \
&lt;span class="n"&gt;copy&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;something_nice_eng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;avi&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary><category term="video"></category><category term="avconv"></category><category term="audio"></category><category term="xbox"></category></entry></feed>